text.section:
Each applicant shall file with the Secretary a statement listing:
The name and address of each applicant and the name and address of the person whose name will appear on the label, if other than the registrant;
The name of the pesticide;
A complete copy of the labeling accompanying the pesticide and a statement of every claim to be made for it, including directions for use; and
A full description of every test conducted and the results upon which any claim is based, if requested by the Secretary.
